Summaries

three sample summaries

[1] Davit Steindl-Rast says that gratefulness makes happiness. Everyone in the world has a desire to be happy, and it is all in common with us. However, the people who are happy don’t have a mind of gratefulness, and the people who have a mind of gratefulness will be happy. Most grateful thing is opportunity because we can’t have a sense of gratitude if we don’t have opportunity.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      
[2] The world’s people think they want to be happy. It’s a common feeling. There is a connection between happiness and gratefulness. It’s not happiness that makes us grateful, it’s gratefulness that makes us happy. It’s important to live gratefully. We should be grateful for an opportunity. Even if we cannot be grateful for every moment, for example violence, war, persecution and exploitation etc, missing the opportunity is bad. When these difficult things occur to us, it’s a challenge. To stand up for your opinion and belief is an opportunity to study, suffer. We only “stop, look, go” in order to live gratefully for the moment. The feeling of gratitude has the potential to change the world. The small group of networks is needed for making the world of gratitude. If more people are grateful for many things, the world will be filled with enjoyment. We can get the chance that make the happy world just by “stop, look, go”                                                
[3] All of us always think “How to be happy?”. What we can do to be happy is common sense. We do not know clearly about the connection between happiness and gratefulness. Many people miss the fortune that others do not have because they are not grateful. Gratefulness makes happiness. Experiences have value for us. These are freely given to us. The key for people is living lives gratefully. For living gratefully, we have to experience something a lot because every moment is a gift which we neither buy nor earn. We should enjoy doing something. Every moment is a new gift, so if we miss the moment, we can get another moment given to us. On the other hand, we cannot be grateful for violence, war, oppression, exploitation, and several friends who are not faithful. The method for how to be happy is composed of three things. “Stop, Look, and Go.” If you pay attention to “Stop, Look, and Go”,you will be able to be grateful and happy. Also we can change our world positively.
3 Levels: All of us always think “How to be happy?”. What we can do to be happy is common sense. We do not know clearly about the connection between happiness and gratefulness. Many people miss the fortune that others do not have because they are not grateful. Gratefulness makes happiness. Experiences have value for us. These are freely given to us. The key for people is living lives gratefully. For living gratefully, we have to experience something a lot because every moment is a gift which we neither buy nor earn.
